STATE
v.
Ralph F. FREDRICK. No. 363P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 27, 2007. Anne M. Middleton, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 23rd day of April 2007 by Defendant for Petition for Rehearing of N.C. Court of Appeals Order:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 27th day of June 2007."
